# ROOT FOLDER POLLUTION PREVENTION
# Only allow these files in root (see CLAUDE.md):
# ✅ CLAUDE.md, README.md, CHANGELOG.md, LICENSE, CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md, SECURITY.md
# ✅ package.json, package-lock.json, tsconfig*.json, jest.config.*, playwright.config.ts
# ✅ .gitignore, .gitattributes, .npmignore, .mermaidrc.json
# ✅ Directories: src/, tests/, plugins/, .specweave/, docs-site/, scripts/, bin/
# ❌ Everything else (*.md reports, *.js scripts, *.log files) → Use increment folders!

# Prevent common root folder violations
/*-SUMMARY*.md
/*-REPORT*.md
/*-ANALYSIS*.md
/*-COMPLETE*.md
/*-GUIDE*.md
/*-FIX*.md
/SESSION-*.md
/IMPLEMENTATION-*.md
/PHASE-*.md
/*.md.backup*
/test-*.js
/debug-*.js

